### Scrape Web Page
POST {{baseUrl}}/scrappings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_intelligence",
  "extract_links": false
}

###

### Generate Embeddings for Existing File
# Replace {{file_id}} with actual file ID from upload/scrape response
POST {{baseUrl}}/embeddings/{{file_id}}

###

### Query Documents (Basic)
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is artificial intelligence?",
  "max_iterations": 2
}

###

### Query with File Filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Explain the main concepts",
  "file_id": "your-file-id-here",
  "max_iterations": 2
}

###

### Query with Source Type Filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Summarize the key points",
  "source_type": "pdf",
  "max_iterations": 3
}

